(80319627, 'U-I-G COLLABORATION', 'U-I-G COLLABORATION', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Dalam rangka pencapaian visi Universitas Hasanuddin (Unhas) sebagai pusat unggulan dalam pengembangan insani, ilmu pengetahuan, teknologi, seni dan budaya berbasis benua maritim Indonesia, maka fakuktas Teknik Unhas membentuk&nbsp; suatu unit kerja yang dikenal dengan nama Center&nbsp; of Technology (CoT). Fungsi utama CoT dimaksudkan untuk mengkoordinir dan menjembatani kerja kolaborasi kemitraan antara Universitas, Industri, dan Pemerintah (U-I-G Collaboration) khususnya di Kawasan Timur Indonesia (KTI).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">For Further Information klik: <a href=\"http://cot.unhas.ac.id\" target=\"_blank\">http://cot.unhas.ac.id</a></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span class=\"tlid-translation translation\"><span title=\"\">In order to achieve the vision of Hasanuddin University (Unhas) as a Center of Excellence in the development of human, scientific, technological, arts and culture based on the Indonesian maritime continent, the Faculty of Engineering Unhas formed a work unit known as the Center of Technology (CoT).</span> <span title=\"\">The main function of the CoT is to coordinate and bridge collaborative work partnerships between the University, Industry and Government (U-I-G </span></span>Collaboration<span class=\"tlid-translation translation\"><span title=\"\">), especially in Eastern Part of Indonesia (EPI).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For Further Information klik: <a href=\"http://cot.unhas.ac.id\">http://cot.unhas.ac.id</a></p>\r\n', 'u-i-g-collaboration', 'u-i-g-collaboration', '', 0, 0, 'added', 0, '2019-01-18 10:08:27', '2019-03-21 05:29:51'),
